title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: An impulsive friend or associate may take happy-go-lucky to new heights today, but that does not mean you should break your stride. Some adjustments might need to be made to account for unexpected fluctuations. A bit of self-discipline works wonders to counteract potential chaos. But otherwise, the tenor of your day is likely to proceed uninterrupted. Just because another persons exploits look entertaining, it doesnt automatically follow that you are tempted to join in. More can be achieved by emulating the industrious ant than the feel-good grasshopper. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
